"<p align=\"right\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; font-weight:700; color:#90caf9;\">155.00 cm</span></p></td></tr>\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td style=\" padding-left:0; padding-right:0; padding-top:4; padding-bottom:4;\">\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color:#b0bec5;\">Diâmetro do estribo (ϕ)</span></p></td>\n"
"<td style=\" padding-left:0; padding-right:0; padding-top:4; padding-bottom:4;\">\n"
"<p align=\"right\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; font-weight:700; color:#90caf9;\">8 mm</span></p></td></tr>\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td style=\" padding-left:0; padding-right:0; padding-top:4; padding-bottom:4;\">\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color:#b0bec5;\">Número de ramos</span></p></td>\n"
"<td style=\" padding-left:0; padding-right:0; padding-top:4; padding-bottom:4;\">\n"
"<p align=\"right\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; font-weight:700; color:#90caf9;\">2</span></p></td></tr></table>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#252525;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; font-size:12pt; color:#b0bec5; background-color:#252525;\">Cálculo do Espaçamento </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:10px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#252525;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0; background-color:#252525;\">1) Área de uma barra: A₁ = π·ϕ²/4 = π·(0.800)²/4 = 0.5027 cm²</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0;\"><br />2) Área total do estribo: A</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0; vertical-align:sub;\">est</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0;\"> = n_ramos · A₁ = 2 · 0.5027 = 1.0053 cm²<br />3) Espaçamento calculado: s</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0; vertical-align:sub;\">calc</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0;\"> = (A</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0; vertical-align:sub;\">est</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0;\"> / A</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0; vertical-align:sub;\">sw</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Courier New\',\'monospace\'; font-size:11pt; color:#e0e0e0;\">) · 100<br />   = (1.0053 / 21.00) · 100 = 4.787 cm </span></p>\n"
"<p style=\" margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; background-color:#252525;\"><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color:#888888; background-color:#252525;\">Arredondamento para baixo com tolerância de 0,5 cm:</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color:#888888;\"><br />s</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color:#888888; vertical-align:sub;\">calculado</span><span style=\" font-family:\'Segoe UI\',\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color:#888888;\"> = 4.787 cm → floor(4.787 × 2) / 2 = 4.5 cm </span></p>\n"
